item.title: Unwanted Godwars Entrance~ HELP!
item.dc:creator: @shmidlap123 shmidlap123
item.description:
@shmidlap123 wrote:

Go into Client.Java, and search the id of the object, until you get something like this:
makeGlobalObject(xcord, ycord, objectid, 0, 10);
And delete that entire line, compile, and it should be fixed.
(make sure the cords are where you are, or it might be another one)

^^317(depending on the version, I guess it might be ‘makeworldobject…’)
